profile_positions.description:
Recruiting volunteers, communicating with the selected volunteers in order to assign them to roles and crews that are appropriate to their skills and abilities, insuring that the volunteers are informed about relevant festival information and events before and during the festival;
managing the scheduling of volunteers as well as solving sudden issues regarding work force;
coordinating the distribution of volunteer t-shirts, volunteer passes and any other required volunteer pack materials and carrying out a volunteer post-festival survey.
